Experience Coastal Luxury: Discover Your Perfect Retreat in Harbour Village. Boat Slip included!  Nestled within the pristine neighborhood of Harbour Village, this stunning 4-bedroom suite custom home invites you into a world of unparalleled elegance and modern comfort. From the moment you step through the entrance, you'll be captivated by the fusion of meticulous architectural craftsmanship and an array of luxurious amenities that redefine living at its finest.Indulge or entertain with the In-Ground Saltwater Pool & unwind in the soothing bubbles of the hot tub. Your personal oasis awaits just steps from your living space, promising endless days of relaxation, fun, and entertainment. Palm trees, crepe myrtles, azaleas, and more contribute to the beauty.Wrap-Around Screened Porch with Breathtaking Views. Enjoy al fresco dining, lounging, and captivating sunsets under the cooling breeze of ceiling fans.30-Foot Deeded Boat Slip at Harbour Village Marina is less than 500 yards and offers an idyllic starting point for aquatic adventures. Cruise along the intracoastal waters or explore the open sea from the marina gateway. Covered parking for your golf cart with charging capability makes trips to the marina a breeze.Gourmet Kitchen & Wine Cabinet with open-concept kitchen, complete with high-end Jenn-Air appliances, a gas oven & stove, built-in wine fridge & cabinet. The additional climate-controlled 820 sq ft bonus room offers versatility as a den, office, fitness space, craft room, or storage area, ensuring your belongings remain pristine and organized.Enjoy the ease of living with 2x propane tanks hard-lined for the stove, oven, fireplace, Generac Back-Up Generator, and BBQ grill.Elevator & Coastal Lifestyle with Outdoor Shower ... too many amenities to mention here.... Ask for the full list! < Experience Coastal Luxury: Discover Your Perfect Retreat in Harbour Village <
Nestled within the pristine neighborhood of Harbour Village, this stunning 4-bedroom suite custom home invites you into a world of unparalleled elegance and modern comfort. From the moment you step through the entrance, you'll be captivated by the fusion of meticulous architectural craftsmanship and an array of luxurious amenities that redefine living at its finest.
<Ê In-Ground Saltwater Pool & Hot Tub <Ê Indulge in resort-style living as you revel in the sparkling embrace of the saltwater pool or unwind in the soothing bubbles of the hot tub. Your personal oasis awaits just steps from your living space, promising endless days of relaxation, fun, and entertainment.
< Wrap-Around Screened Porch with Breathtaking Views < Elevate your outdoor experience on the expansive wrap-around screened porch, offering panoramic views of the serene surroundings. Enjoy al fresco dining, lounging, and captivating sunsets under the cooling breeze of ceiling fans.
=å 30-Foot Boat Slip at Harbour Village Marina =å For water enthusiasts, a private boat slip at Harbour Village Marina offers an idyllic starting point for aquatic adventures. Cruise along the intracoastal waters or explore the open sea from the marina gateway.
<w Gourmet Kitchen & Wine Cabinet <w Unleash your inner culinary artist in the open-concept kitchen, complete with high-end Jenn-Air appliances, a gas oven, and stove. The built-in wine cabinet seamlessly combines style and functionality for the connoisseur in you.
=% Gas Fireplace & Vaulted Ceiling =% Step inside to discover a warm and inviting ambiance, with a gas fireplace as the heart of your living space. The vaulted ceiling adds a touch of grandeur, creating an atmosphere perfect for intimate gatherings or lavish celebrations.
=× Elevator & Climate-Controlled Bonus Space =× Accessibility meets convenience with a built-in elevator, effortlessly connecting every floor. The additional climate-controlled 820 sq ft bonus room offers versatility as a den, office, fitness space, craft room, or storage area, ensuring your belongings remain pristine and organized.
=¨ Propane-Powered Convenience and ¡ Generac Back-Up Generator ¡ Enjoy the ease of living with 2x propane tanks hard-lined for the stove, oven, fireplace, Generac, and BBQ grill. Experience uninterrupted tranquility with the Generac back-up generator, guaranteeing a seamless power supply during unforeseen outages.
=¿ Coastal Lifestyle with Outdoor Shower =¿ Embrace the coastal ambiance with an invigorating outdoor shower, a perfect way to rinse off after a day at the beach or a refreshing dip in the pool. High-end Hunter Douglas blinds will keep your home cool and looking great.
<3 Professional Landscaping for an Outdoor Oasis <3 Step into an outdoor entertainment oasis with professionally landscaped surroundings. Palm trees, crepe myrtles, azaleas, and more contribute to the beauty of your living environment.
=— Convenient Covered Parking =— A 2-car garage with a custom floor and insulated doors offers secure parking. Additionally, covered parking for your golf cart with charging capability makes trips to the marina a breeze.
